---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-zinc-900 via-primary to-zinc-800 text-white">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute left-1/3 top-10 h-72 w-72 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400/20 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 h-80 w-80 translate-x-1/3 rounded-full bg-purple-500/20 blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-start gap-12 px-4 py-24 sm:px-6 lg:flex-row lg:items-center">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-white/60">Product Preview</p>
        <h1 class="mt-5 text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight sm:text-5xl">
          Keero — Calm Knowledge Sharing for Product Teams
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg text-white/80">
          Keero helps remote product teams turn scattered notes and decisions into a collective memory. Centralized updates,
          async rituals, and contextual handoffs keep everyone aligned without endless calls.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <a
            href="#request-access"
            class="rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary transition hover:bg-white/90"
          >
            Request Early Access
          </a>
          <a
            href="#features"
            class="rounded-full border border-white/30 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white/80 transition hover:border-white hover:text-white"
          >
            Explore Features
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col gap-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/10 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/10 backdrop-blur">
        <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/60">Snapshot</span>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-black/20 p-6 text-sm text-white/80">
          <p class="font-semibold text-white">Weekly Rhythm in Keero</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
            <li>• Monday playback recorded asynchronously</li>
            <li>• Mid-week focus check with lightweight reactions</li>
            <li>• Friday learnings exported for leadership digest</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white">12</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/60">Pilot Teams</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white">28%</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/60">Less Sync Time</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-white/50">Launch window: Q1 2026</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="features" class="bg-white py-16 dark:bg-primary/95">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-primary/50 dark:text-white/50">Why Keero</p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-semibold text-primary dark:text-white">Knowledge that Keeps Moving Forward</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-primary/70 dark:text-white/70">
          Keero sits between docs, chat, and project trackers—making sure product decisions stay visible and actionable.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-primary/10 bg-zinc-50 p-8 shadow-sm dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary dark:text-white">Contextual Briefings</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-primary/70 dark:text-white/70">
            Automate weekly briefings that highlight what changed, why decisions were made, and what needs attention.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-primary/60 dark:text-white/60">
            <li>• Connect product specs, tickets, and research</li>
            <li>• Generate shareable snapshots for stakeholders</li>
            <li>• Track decisions with inline commentary</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-primary/10 bg-zinc-50 p-8 shadow-sm dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary dark:text-white">Async Rituals</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-primary/70 dark:text-white/70">
            Replace status meetings with focused prompts, timeboxed responses, and automatic rollups.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-primary/60 dark:text-white/60">
            <li>• Lightweight prompts for squads and leaders</li>
            <li>• Smart reminders for overdue updates</li>
            <li>• Mood and confidence tracking across initiatives</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-primary/10 bg-zinc-50 p-8 shadow-sm dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary dark:text-white">Connected Outcomes</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-primary/70 dark:text-white/70">
            Surface learnings, metrics, and next bets from every iteration to keep the roadmap grounded.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-primary/60 dark:text-white/60">
            <li>• Link experiment results and research snippets</li>
            <li>• Build a searchable library of insights</li>
            <li>• Celebrate wins with automated spotlights</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-primary/10 bg-zinc-50 p-8 shadow-sm dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary dark:text-white">Secure Collaboration</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-primary/70 dark:text-white/70">
            Manage guests, fine-grained permissions, and export controls for regulated teams.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-primary/60 dark:text-white/60">
            <li>• SOC2-ready infrastructure baseline</li>
            <li>• SSO and SCIM on growth-tier plans</li>
            <li>• Audit trails and compliance-friendly logging</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-zinc-100 py-16 dark:bg-primary">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:gap-16">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-primary/50 dark:text-white/50">Workflows</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-primary dark:text-white">Designed for Product R&D Loops</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-primary/70 dark:text-white/70">
            Keero pulls together insights across discovery, delivery, and launch. Highlight what to explore further or where
            experiments need a boost.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-primary/60 dark:text-white/60">
            <li>• Research insights connect directly to roadmap initiatives.</li>
            <li>• Meeting notes sync back to the relevant squads instantly.</li>
            <li>• Lightweight rituals keep leadership in the loop without micromanaging.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 rounded-3xl border border-primary/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-lg shadow-primary/10 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5 dark:shadow-black/10">
          <div class="space-y-5 text-sm text-primary/70 dark:text-white/70">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-primary/50 dark:text-white/50">Sample Flow</p>
              <p class="mt-2 font-semibold text-primary dark:text-white">Discovery → Decision → Delivery</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 p-4 dark:bg-white/10">
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-primary/60 dark:text-white/60">1. Discovery Pulse</p>
              <p class="mt-2">
                Researchers log new findings, tag personas, and assign confidence scores. Keero suggests related decisions.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 p-4 dark:bg-white/10">
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-primary/60 dark:text-white/60">2. Decision Canvas</p>
              <p class="mt-2">PMs capture trade-offs, link specs, and request async approvals with reactions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 p-4 dark:bg-white/10">
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-primary/60 dark:text-white/60">3. Delivery Digest</p>
              <p class="mt-2">Engineering leads post progress snapshots, blockers, and need-to-knows for launch partners.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-zinc-100 py-16 dark:bg-primary">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr] lg:gap-16">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-primary/50 dark:text-white/50">Voices</p>
          <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-semibold text-primary dark:text-white">What early partners are saying</h2>
          <div class="mt-8 space-y-6">
            <figure class="rounded-3xl border border-primary/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5">
              <blockquote class="text-primary/70 dark:text-white/70">
                “Keero gave our PMs a single weekly ritual. Leadership still gets context, but the team keeps their focus time.”
              </blockquote>
              <figcaption class="mt-4 text-sm text-primary/60 dark:text-white/60">
                Anja, Head of Product Ops @ Driftline
              </figcaption>
            </figure>
            <figure class="rounded-3xl border border-primary/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5">
              <blockquote class="text-primary/70 dark:text-white/70">
                “Syncing roadmap and research used to mean five tools. Keero made the story clear in one place.”
              </blockquote>
              <figcaption class="mt-4 text-sm text-primary/60 dark:text-white/60">
                Leo, Group Product Manager @ Northwind
              </figcaption>
            </figure>
          </div>
        </div>
        <aside class="rounded-3xl border border-primary/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-primary/50 dark:text-white/50">Tech Stack</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-primary/70 dark:text-white/70">
            <li>• Real-time sync via Supabase + PostgreSQL</li>
            <li>• Next.js edge functions for prompt responses</li>
            <li>• Rich document editing with TipTap</li>
            <li>• AI summaries powered by OpenAI GPT-4.1</li>
          </ul>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-16 dark:bg-primary/95">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-primary/50 dark:text-white/50">Integrations</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-primary dark:text-white">Connect the tools your squads already love</h2>
        <p class="max-w-3xl text-primary/70 dark:text-white/70">
          Keero keeps data flowing without duplicate work. Bring in updates from delivery tools and push highlights back to the
          rest of the company.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-primary/10 bg-zinc-50 p-5 text-primary/70 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5 dark:text-white/70">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary dark:text-white">Linear</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Sync project status, auto-link issues, and surface upcoming releases in weekly recaps.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-primary/10 bg-zinc-50 p-5 text-primary/70 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5 dark:text-white/70">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary dark:text-white">Notion</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Embed Keero briefings into docs or pull existing specs into a decision canvas in one click.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-primary/10 bg-zinc-50 p-5 text-primary/70 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5 dark:text-white/70">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary dark:text-white">Slack</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Deliver bite-sized summaries to stakeholder channels and gather reactions asynchronously.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-primary/10 bg-zinc-50 p-5 text-primary/70 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5 dark:text-white/70">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary dark:text-white">Figma</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Attach design prototypes to rituals, track reviews, and capture decision history inline.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="request-access" class="bg-primary text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-4xl flex-col gap-6 px-4 py-16 text-center sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Be the first to know when Keero launches</h2>
      <p class="text-white/80">
        Drop your email to join the early access list. We share monthly updates, design previews, and beta invitations.
      </p>
      <form class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-md flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <input
          type="email"
          placeholder="you@team.com"
          class="flex-1 rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-white/10 px-5 py-3 text-sm text-white placeholder-white/50 focus:border-white focus:outline-none"
          required
        />
        <button type="submit" class="rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary hover:bg-white/90">
          Join Waitlist
        </button>
      </form>
      <p class="text-xs text-white/50">No spam. Just product updates and invites.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

